		"name": "Financial Transaction System",
		"description": "## Authentication\nUse **Bearer Token** (Laravel Sanctum). Set the `token` collection variable.\n\nLogin/register HTTP routes are not registered in this app yet (`AuthController` exists but is not wired). Create a token with `php artisan tinker`, e.g. `\\Modules\\User\\Models\\User::first()?->createToken('postman')->plainTextToken`, or add routes to `Modules\\User\\Http\\Controllers\\API\\AuthController`.\n\n## Base URL\nDefault `base_url` is `http://localhost:8000` — adjust for your environment.\n\n## Plaid\nProtected Plaid routes use the default `api` guard (Sanctum). The webhook has **no** Bearer auth.",
		"schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
	},
